			<title>C++/Qt developer - Institute for Scientific Interchange</title>
			<link>https://www.openscenegraph.com/index.php/community/jobs/job-offers/168-c-qt-developer-institute-for-scientific-interchange</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.openscenegraph.com/index.php/community/jobs/job-offers/168-c-qt-developer-institute-for-scientific-interchange</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 16.8999996185303px;">The Computational Epidemiology &amp; Public Health group of the <span class="caps" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">ISI</span> Foundation (<a href="http://www.isi.it%29/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">http://www.isi.it)</a> is looking for an experienced C++ developer to be included in the team.</p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 16.8999996185303px;">The main development activity will be related to the the client application that is part of the <span class="caps" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">GLEAM</span>viz Simulator project (<a href="http://www.gleamviz.org/simulator/)." style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">http://www.gleamviz.org/simulator/).</a> The GLEAMviz client makes heavy usage of the OSG toolkit -integrated within the Qt framework- for data visualisation.</p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 16.8999996185303px;">Required qualifications:</p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">3+ years of working experience as a software developer;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">good knowledge of C++;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">knowledge of the Qt framework;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">knowledge of openSceneGraph and OpenGL;</span></li>
<li><span class="caps" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">OOP</span><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">event driven programming;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">english language (spoken and written).</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;"> </span></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 16.8999996185303px;">Preferred qualifications:</p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">working experience in 2D/3D graphics programming;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">working experience with the Qt framework;</span></li>
<li><span class="caps" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">GUI</span><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;"> development;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">experience with other languages (Java, Python, …);</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16.8999996185303px; background-color: initial;">network programming.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 16.8999996185303px;"> </p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 16.8999996185303px;">Good attitude for team working and self management skills are also required.<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />Occupation: full time.<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />Workplace: Turin, Italy (Computational Epidemiology Lab, <span class="caps" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">ISI</span> Foundation).</p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 16.8999996185303px;">Applications should be sent to:<span style="color: #747474; font-family: Merriweather, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px;"> </span><a href="mailto:corrado.gioannini@isi.it" style="font-family: Merriweather, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; color: #333333 !important;">gioannini@isi.it</a></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 16.8999996185303px;">Ref: <a href="http://www.isi.it/open-position-isi-2/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">http://www.isi.it/open-position-isi-2/</a></p>]]></description>
